Variables:
- teamMembers: Array<any> - holds the data source for the table
- displayedColumns: string[] - holds the column names to be displayed in the table

Constants:
- mat-h2: string - a CSS class name for styling the h2 element
- mat-elevation-z8: string - a CSS class name for styling the table element

ViewChild:
- None

Functions:
- applyFilter(filterValue: string): void - filters the data source based on the input value and updates the table

Mat-table column names (constants):
- name: string - the column name for the member's name
- email: string - the column name for the member's email
- role: string - the column name for the member's role